videos.description: Indiana's inbounds attempt in order to set up a game-tying 3-pointer is intercepted, resulting in the Fort Wayne fans storming the court after beating the No. 3 ranked Hoosiers.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Fort Wayne storms the court after beating No. 3 Indiana) 2016/11/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: Fort Wayne storms the court after beating No. 3 Indiana

videos.description: Fort Wayne basketball coach Jon Coffman credits Indiana for coming to play in Fort Wayne and is amazed his team was able to win despite shooting 7-for-31 from 3-point range.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Interview (Fort Wayne coach amazed at win despite off-shooting night) 2016/11/22 ESHEET SC

videos.headline: Fort Wayne coach amazed at win despite off-shooting night
